239
00:29:58,679 --> 00:30:01,158
Frank.

240
00:30:02,318 --> 00:30:03,278
Frank!

241
00:30:05,479 --> 00:30:06,518
Frank!

242
00:30:06,719 --> 00:30:11,599
Not what you expected when you reported
for work this morning, is it, Frank? No?

243
00:30:11,919 --> 00:30:14,799
Is that what passes for wit in this circle?

244
