- Stay calm.

393
00:47:25,877 --> 00:47:27,797
- It's my son!
- Let them work.

394
00:47:27,998 --> 00:47:30,758
- Are you gonna sit and do nothing?
- They're experts.

395
00:47:30,958 --> 00:47:34,518
Everyone is an expert!
I've had it with all of you!

396
00:47:34,798 --> 00:47:36,158
Audrey!

397
00:47:39,519 --> 00:47:41,718
Audrey!

398
00:47:41,998 --> 00:47:43,518
Audrey!

399
00:47:48,119 --> 00:47:49,559
Audrey!

400
00:47:51,879 --> 00:47:54,078
Mommy!

