00:47:56,478 --> 00:47:58,479
Jack!

402
00:47:59,159 --> 00:48:01,279
Are you OK?

403
00:48:06,079 --> 00:48:08,759
There you go, little buddy.

404
00:48:12,880 --> 00:48:15,760
Breathe. Come on, breathe.

