447
00:54:41,708 --> 00:54:43,907
With Jack...

448
00:54:44,108 --> 00:54:46,588
and with you.

449
00:54:48,988 --> 00:54:53,708
- Are you OK?
- Mr. Billings. We're running late.

450
00:54:53,988 --> 00:54:58,988
I'll be right out.
I'd like to come by after the conference,

451
00:54:59,148 --> 00:55:01,828
check on Jack.

452
00:55:02,028 --> 00:55:04,149
Check on you.

453
00:55:06,069 --> 00:55:09,309
Good. I'll see you soon.

454
00:55:09,509 --> 00:55:11,709
They're here if you need them.

455
00:55:23,349 --> 00:55:26,589
- Are you all right, ma'am?
